title: #103: The Lost City of Atlantis with Those Conspiracy Guys' Gordon Rochford
description: Thank you for tuning into for another crazy episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli.  This episode, Sam and Ryan, welcome from the awesome podcast "Those Conspiracy Guys," the one and only Gordo Rochford, to discuss the lost city of Atlantis.  Thank you so much for you support.
